<div class="txtlevel"><p>Proiect de testare pentru studentii din grupa 234.</p></div>
 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : meir3555_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Suita&nbsp;de teste black-box pentru cerinta F01 - adaugarea produselor&nbsp;in MyDrinkShop.<br />
Include 4 cazuri de testare: ECP valid, ECP invalid, BVA valid, BVA invalid.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29007"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-11: meir3555_ECP_Valid_AddProduct&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">meir3555</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verifica&nbsp;adaugarea unui produs nou cu date valide din clase de echivalenta&nbsp;valide.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Administratorul este in&nbsp;ecranul de gestionare produse.<br />
Exista&nbsp;cel putin o reteta&nbsp;selectabila&nbsp;in tabelul de retete.<br />
Nu exista&nbsp;deja un produs cu ID-ul retetei selectate.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>1. Se selecteaza&nbsp;o reteta&nbsp;existenta&nbsp;din tabelul de retete.<br />
2. Se introduce numele produsului: Latte.<br />
3. Se introduce pretul: 15.5.<br />
4. Se selecteaza&nbsp;categoria: MILK_COFFEE.<br />
5. Se selecteaza&nbsp;tipul: DAIRY.<br />
6. Se apasa&nbsp;butonul Add.</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul este adaugat cu succes.<br />
Produsul apare in lista de produse.<br />
Valorile salvate sunt:<br />
- nume = Latte<br />
- pret&nbsp;= 15.5<br />
- categorie = MILK_COFFEE<br />
- tip = DAIRY<br />
- ID = ID-ul retetei selectate.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">meir3555_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29013"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-12: meir3555_ECP_Invalid_AddProduct_BlankName&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">meir3555</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verifica&nbsp;respingerea adaugarii unui produs nou cu nume invalid (gol).</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Administratorul este in ecranul de gestionare produse.<br />
Exista&nbsp;cel putin o reteta&nbsp;selectabila&nbsp;in tabelul de retete.<br />
Nu exista&nbsp;deja un produs cu ID-ul retetei selectate.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>1. Se selecteaza&nbsp;o reteta&nbsp;existenta&nbsp;din tabelul de retete.<br />
2. Se introduce numele produsului: &quot; &quot; (blank).<br />
3. Se introduce pretul: 12.0.<br />
4. Se selecteaza&nbsp;categoria: CLASSIC_COFFEE.<br />
5. Se selecteaza&nbsp;tipul: BASIC.<br />
6. Se apasa&nbsp;butonul Add.</p>
</td><td><p>Sistemul trebuie sa&nbsp;respinga&nbsp;adaugarea produsului.<br />
Se afiseaza&nbsp;un mesaj de eroare privind numele invalid.<br />
Produsul nu este salvat si nu apare in lista de produse.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">meir3555_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29016"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-13: meir3555_BVA_Valid_AddProduct_PriceAboveZero&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
